26
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:23,120
However, on the detonating cord,

27
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:23,880
detonator,

28
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,079
and bomb fragments left at the scene,

29
00:02:25,079 --> 00:02:27,210
