37
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:50,370
installed, and detonated by Ma Jinguang.

38
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,530
Only Ma Jinguang's?

39
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:54,720
Other than Wang Hongjia,

40
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:55,240
Yan Mi,

41
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:56,040
and Ma Jinguang,

42
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:58,079
were there no traces of a fourth person at the scene?

43
00:02:58,079 --> 00:02:59,079
Not at the moment.

44
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:00,360
Keep investigating.

45
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:02,080
Since Yan Mi said

46
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:04,760
Ma Jinguang didn't commit Wang Hongjia's murder,

47
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:05,560
then that day,

48
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:08,320
