49
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:10,380
Leave no stone unturned to find them.

50
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:11,490
Captain Sun.

51
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:12,640
Keep looking.

52
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:13,360
Be thorough.

53
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:13,890
Yes, sir.

54
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:24,600
If Ma Jinguang didn't do these,

55
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:27,360
