62
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:43,280
After testing,

63
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,160
these residues

64
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:46,760
have the same composition as those in Zhang Biao's bombing case.

65
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:47,960
It can be reasonably inferred.

66
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,760
Ma Jinguang was making explosives

67
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:50,490
in the cabin.

68
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,280
Combined with

69
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,760
some of his previous confessions,

70
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:54,440
we can

71
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:55,720
reasonably conclude that

72
00:03:55,720 --> 00:03:57,120
Ma Jinguang was

73
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,360
the explosives provider for the Zhou Gang bombing five years ago,

74
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,200
as well as the current

75
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:00,120
Zhang Biao

76
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:00,920
bombing case.

77
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:04,000
Just providing explosives?

78
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:07,440
Did he specifically

79
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,680
