80
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:13,040
Evidence shows

81
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:16,370
that the one who murdered Wang Hongjia

82
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,370
couldn't be him.

83
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:19,720
Although in this mine explosion,

84
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:20,959
the clothes he wore

85
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,880
and those captured on surveillance

86
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:25,010
during the kidnapping of Wang Hongjia

87
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,160
are exactly the same,

88
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,200
the current evidence

89
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:28,860
cannot form a complete chain.

90
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,120
Furthermore,

91
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:32,440
currently, both Wang Hongjia

92
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:33,300
and Ma Jinguang

93
