94
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:37,930
Until we get more information,

95
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,159
we cannot make

96
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,130
any further judgments.

97
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:50,159
We haven't found the killer.

98
00:04:51,640 --> 00:04:54,300
Instead, we're finding more and more problems.

99
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:56,850
Yan Mi also got injured,

100
00:04:58,320 --> 00:04:59,240
guys.

101
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:03,290
I've also worked in criminal investigation.

102
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,280
I have walked all the paths

103
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:07,410
you are walking now.

104
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,200
So I can understand

105
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:13,400
everyone's hardships,

106
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,760
and I keep them in mind.

107
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:17,000
But coming back to the point.

108
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:18,800
As a police officer,

109
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:22,040
if you can't solve cases,

110
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,560
no matter how much hardship you endure

111
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,800
or how many injuries you suffer,

112
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,240
