122
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,920
We must be thorough and detailed.

123
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,560
Don't miss anything.

124
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,890
I am counting on you all.

125
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:57,780
Chief Zhao,

126
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,180
there's something

127
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,580
I hope you can approve.

128
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:03,980
What are you doing?

129
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:06,160
Are you trying to undermine me?

130
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,620
I just finished speaking,

131
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,520
