132
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,720
I will never back out.

133
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,880
I will definitely investigate this case to the end.

134
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:13,960
Then I still don't understand.

135
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:15,080
What do you mean by this?

136
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:15,940
Five years ago,

137
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:17,960
I was the lead investigator of Zhou Gang's case.

138
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:18,760
Now we found

139
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,960
that the chain of evidence is indeed flawed.

140
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:23,620
I should be held accountable.

141
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:26,100
Whether you are held accountable

142
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,400
or how you are held accountable,

143
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:29,000
is not for you to worry about.

144
00:06:29,080 --> 00:06:29,760
For you,

145
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:30,600
the most important thing right now

146
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:32,200
is how you view your mistakes

147
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:34,760
and whether you have the courage and determination to correct them.

148
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:36,220
Learn from your mistakes,

149
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,280
take honesty as a warning,

150
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:39,080
and don't make another mistake.

151
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:41,120
Chief Zhao,

152
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:41,440
alright,

153
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:41,760
I...

154
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:43,080
Stop saying useless things.

155
00:06:43,080 --> 00:06:44,810
Just focus on solving the case.

156
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,180
By the end of the month,

157
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:53,170
