158
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,520
I will take off this uniform.

159
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:00,600
This is what was on Wang Hongjia's body.

160
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:00,960
Yes.

161
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:03,280
This is the mycelium of a fungus called Mycena haematopus.

162
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:05,920
It can emit a pale green fluorescence in the dark.

163
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:07,380
But the light is very weak,

164
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:09,580
so it's hard to see with the naked eye.

165
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:11,640
Glowing mushrooms.

166
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:14,280
After going to such great lengths,

167
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:16,440
what exactly is the killer trying to say?

168
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,440
Come look at this.

169
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:24,280
The killer cut open Wang Hongjia's skin

170
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:26,720
and attached mycelium to the wound,

171
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:29,680
giving it the appearance of a scar.

172
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:32,320
And this Mycena haematopus

173
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:34,960
is also known as the bleeding fairy helmet.

174
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,120
It has a unique trait.

175
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,159
When damaged,

176
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,400
it will ooze from the wound

177
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:40,920
a blood-like,

178
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,120
dark red liquid.

179
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:43,720
Scar.

180
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:48,610
Bleeding from the head.

181
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:02,520
In that case,

182
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:05,140
the killer wants not only to torture,

183
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,290
but also to destroy.

184
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:09,560
Baby,

185
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:11,080
let's take the medicine, okay?

186
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:11,760
No.

187
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:12,880
It's too bitter.

188
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:13,960
Be a good boy and

189
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:14,960
take the medicine.

190
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,560
No,

191
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:17,640
I don't want to take it.

192
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:19,120
Why are you being like this?

193
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,600
How will you get better without taking your medicine?

194
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,920
I don't have that much money to waste here.

195
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:23,400
Listen to me.

196
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:24,360
You sit right here.

197
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,680
I'm going to find the nurse to get the medicine.

198
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,480
Do you hear me?

199
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:02,880
Woof.

200
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,440
Take it if you like it.

201
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:10,210
It's for you.

202
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:11,480
Be good and take your medicine.

203
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:13,610
You can go out to play once you recover.

204
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,320
This is for you.

205
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:25,560
Thank you.

206
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:28,400
Thanks.

207
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:32,720
So sweet.

208
00:09:57,160 --> 00:09:58,840
Family of Yan Mi in bed 14.

209
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:00,620
Please come over and sign.

210
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:01,260
Coming.

211
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:36,960
Yan Mi.

212
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:39,520
You're still alive.

213
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:43,560
True.

214
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,640
It's good to be alive.

215
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:55,000
Make sure you don't die so soon.

216
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:58,040
I haven't had enough fun yet.

217
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:07,370
Guannan.

218
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:09,080
When did you get here?

219
00:11:09,160 --> 00:11:10,960
We don't allow visitors for now.

220
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,320
I'm sorry.

221
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:15,960
Mi.

222
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:17,600
Get well soon.

223
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:21,540
The bad guys are still waiting for you to catch them.

224
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:25,090
Sorry to bother you.

225
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:42,920
Thank you, Uncle.

226
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:50,840
Thank you, Uncle.

227
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:52,280
Here.

228
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:52,880
Thank you.

229
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:53,810
You're welcome.

230
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:05,880
Wait.

231
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:07,160
Where is he?

232
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:08,760
Didn't they say he wasn't in danger?

233
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:10,220
Why did they wheel him out?

234
00:12:10,520 --> 00:12:11,840
The guy in the next bed,

235
00:12:11,880 --> 00:12:12,760
