236
00:12:12,760 --> 00:12:13,920
I couldn't stop him.

237
00:12:21,280 --> 00:12:22,280
I know where he is.

238
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:25,210
Hey, Master.

239
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:27,840
I'm speechless.

240
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,000
Old Yan.

241
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:12,400
Is your injury healed?

242
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:14,260
You shouldn't be running around.

243
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:15,400
Come back with me

244
00:13:15,400 --> 00:13:16,130
and recover.

245
00:13:16,160 --> 00:13:16,920
I'm fine.

246
00:13:17,520 --> 00:13:18,360
I can walk,

247
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:19,220
and I can think.

248
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:22,320
The detonator found at the scene,

249
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:23,240
