250
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:23,970
Old Wang said

251
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:25,320
it was triggered by a detonating cord.

252
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:25,920
The detonating cord

253
00:13:25,920 --> 00:13:26,960
and the bomb fragments

254
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:28,090
have all been found.

255
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:30,620
Ma Jinguang's fingerprints are on them.

256
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:35,060
No remote control device was found at the scene.

257
00:13:35,520 --> 00:13:37,780
Ma Jinguang didn't press the detonator.

258
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:39,570
The killer was at the scene.

259
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:42,480
There must have been another detonating cord.

260
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,880
But after the explosion,

261
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,540
the killer pulled it away,

262
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,360
so it wasn't found.

263
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,460
It's possible.

264
00:13:48,920 --> 00:13:50,000
But so far at the scene,

265
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:52,600
we haven't found any traces of a fourth person.

266
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:48,320
The left footprint is deep, and the right is shallow.

267
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:50,240
His dominant weight-bearing foot is the left.

268
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:51,440
He should have a limp.

269
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:52,840
In this case,

270
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:55,360
in the previous case of Qiao Sisi,

271
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:56,760
the person who took the taxi

272
00:14:56,760 --> 00:14:57,820
that we didn't find

273
00:14:58,280 --> 00:14:59,610
is quite similar to him.

274
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,000
Call Mr. Wang over,

275
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:05,120
tell him to bring the equipment,

276
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:05,960
and let him know

277
00:15:05,960 --> 00:15:08,160
there's a problem with the footprints.

278
00:15:10,640 --> 00:15:11,760
His previous crimes

279
00:15:11,760 --> 00:15:13,320
were planned so meticulously

280
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:15,180
that he almost erased all traces.

281
00:15:15,560 --> 00:15:16,620
Why did he suddenly

282
00:15:16,800 --> 00:15:18,360
leave two behind this time?

283
00:15:18,920 --> 00:15:19,580
Wood chips.

284
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:22,370
Such an obvious piece of information.

285
00:15:22,760 --> 00:15:23,760
You mean

286
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:25,800
this is another false target?

287
00:15:25,800 --> 00:15:26,400
The killer

288
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:29,420
wants to continuously create false targets

289
00:15:29,680 --> 00:15:31,560
to consume our time and energy,

290
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:34,240
trying to control the pace of this game.

291
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:35,040
What exactly

292
00:15:36,160 --> 00:15:37,240
is he trying to do?

293
00:15:47,520 --> 00:15:48,080
Yan,

294
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:52,840
I take our master's case from five years ago

295
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:53,850
very seriously.

296
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:55,560
But

297
00:15:55,560 --> 00:15:56,890
it's my responsibility

298
00:15:57,480 --> 00:15:58,940
that I didn't investigate

299
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:01,700
the source of the explosives carefully.

300
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:03,680
Ma Jinguang was

301
00:16:03,680 --> 00:16:05,080
the bomb maker back then.

302
00:16:05,960 --> 00:16:06,880
I missed him.

303
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:09,650
Your persistence is right.

304
00:16:10,680 --> 00:16:12,280
It also proves that Ma Jinguang

305
00:16:12,280 --> 00:16:14,410
is the one who slipped through the net.

306
00:16:14,680 --> 00:16:17,200
Actually, Guannan was right to scold me that day.

307
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:17,880
He

308
00:16:18,240 --> 00:16:19,200
woke me up.

309
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,800
The killer committed suicide to escape punishment.

310
00:16:20,800 --> 00:16:22,520
This answer is too simple, isn't it?

311
00:16:22,520 --> 00:16:25,240
So simple that it can't hold your guilt and pain.

312
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:28,520
So you endlessly want to prove there is another real killer.

313
00:16:28,520 --> 00:16:30,600
Actually, you just want to find a scapegoat

314
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:32,320
to make yourself feel better,

315
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:34,880
so you can escape your own guilt.

316
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,320
If no one is wrong,

317
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:37,400
then who is wrong?

318
00:16:37,760 --> 00:16:38,800
Me?

319
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:42,620
Ma Jinguang provided the bomb without knowing.

320
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:44,920
This is actually not the truth.

321
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:47,240
At best, it's just

322
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:48,600
an answer,

323
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:50,780
an answer that makes me see

324
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:52,640
how cowardly I am.

325
00:16:53,400 --> 00:16:55,000
I held on to those doubts

326
00:16:55,320 --> 00:16:57,600
because I dared not face the fact

327
00:16:57,920 --> 00:17:00,000
that I handed the car keys to our master.

328
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:01,200
The real killer I hate

329
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:02,320
is actually the me

330
00:17:02,440 --> 00:17:04,900
who should have been in the car but survived.

331
00:17:05,359 --> 00:17:07,319
Closing the case back then wasn't wrong.

332
00:17:07,319 --> 00:17:07,920
It was me

333
00:17:08,280 --> 00:17:10,520
who didn't want to accept this simple cruelty.

334
00:17:10,520 --> 00:17:12,319
Now we've found the real killer.

335
00:17:12,800 --> 00:17:13,720
Living to bear

336
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:14,680
this guilt

337
00:17:16,319 --> 00:17:17,040
requires more courage

338
00:17:17,040 --> 00:17:18,119
than dying.

339
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:20,619
From now on,

340
00:17:20,800 --> 00:17:22,560
bear the responsibilities you should bear.

341
00:17:22,560 --> 00:17:23,800
Do what you should do.

342
00:17:24,359 --> 00:17:26,079
This is the best explanation

343
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:27,480
for our master, his wife,

344
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:28,480
and Guannan.

345
00:17:29,320 --> 00:17:29,920
Yan.

346
00:17:30,280 --> 00:17:32,600
This reconciliation you've reached with yourself

347
00:17:32,600 --> 00:17:34,320
is the most precious growth.

348
00:17:35,120 --> 00:17:37,160
I hope you and Sun Xun can take our master's

349
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:38,800
unfinished glory

350
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:40,450
and carry on.

351
00:17:52,360 --> 00:17:53,360
Let's get back to the case.

352
00:17:53,360 --> 00:17:55,320
We identified the mycelium on Wang Hongjia.

353
00:17:55,320 --> 00:17:56,680
It's a poisonous mushroom

354
00:17:56,680 --> 00:17:58,810
that bleeds from its cap when injured.

355
00:18:00,240 --> 00:18:02,120
The killer specifically found this mushroom,

356
00:18:02,120 --> 00:18:03,760
and he is obsessed with

357
00:18:03,760 --> 00:18:06,160
striking his victims' heads during the crimes.

358
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:07,480
It's hard not to assume

359
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:10,520
he's making a metaphor for the previous cases.

360
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:16,540
Another elaborate setup.

361
00:18:17,080 --> 00:18:17,960
This footprint

362
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:20,140
is more like a warning.

363
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:22,320
It's telling us

364
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:25,880
a new round of the game

365
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:27,800
is about to begin.
